Early life and education[edit]
Martin Stuart Sorrell was born in London on 14 February 1945 to a Jewish family with an electronics retailer father,[3][4] whose ancestors came from Russia, Poland and Romania,[5] Sorrell was educated at the independent Haberdashers' Aske's Boys' School then Christ's College, Cambridge, and has an MBA from Harvard University.[3][6]
